Project Description

NUnit Results Explorer allows the viewing of NUnit XML result files.

It is written in C#/WPF.

It currently targets NUnit 2.5.7.

NUnit Results Explorer is still under initial development, but the current source base should work reasonably.

Please see the documentation to find out how to get started.
